==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Overeat
<hw>O`ver*eat"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>To gnaw all over, or on all sides.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To eat to excess; -- sometimes with a reflexive;
<as>as, she <ex>overate</ex> at the party and spent the next week
dieting</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overelegant</ent>⟦br⟧
